<div id="title-container">
<h1 class="title col-full">The Journey to Bhutan: Flying Over the Himalayas</h1>
</div>
<div id="content" class="col-full">
<p class="panete-meta">
<span class="panete-date"><span class="small">Posted on</span> December 12, 2013</span>
<span class="panete-author"><span class="small">by</span> <a href="http://www.wildjunket.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Nellie Huang" rel="author">Nellie Huang</a></span>‹
</p>
<div id="main" class="col-left">
<a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="http://www.wildjunket.com/2013/12/12/the-journey-to-bhutan-flying-over-the-himalayas/" data-count="horizontal" data-text="The Journey to Bhutan: Flying Over the Himalayas" data-via="wildjunket"></a><script type="text/javascript" src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js"></script><iframe src='http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildjunket.com%2F2013%2F12%2F12%2Fthe-journey-to-bhutan-flying-over-the-himalayas%2F&amp;locale=&amp;layout=button_count&amp;action=like&amp;width=92&amp;height=20&amp;colorscheme=light' scrolling='no' frameborder='0' style='border:none; overflow:hidden; width:92px; height:20px;' allowTransparency='true'></iframe><script type='text/javascript' src='https://apis.google.com/js/plusone.js'></script><g:plusone size='medium' href='http://www.wildjunket.com/2013/12/12/the-journey-to-bhutan-flying-over-the-himalayas/'></g:plusone><script src='http://www.stumbleupon.com/hostedbadge.php?s=1&amp;r=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildjunket.com%2F2013%2F12%2F12%2Fthe-journey-to-bhutan-flying-over-the-himalayas%2F'></script><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wildjunket.com%2F2013%2F12%2F12%2Fthe-journey-to-bhutan-flying-over-the-himalayas%2F&description=The%20Journey%20to%20Bhutan%3A%20Flying%20Over%20the%20Himalayas&media=" class="pin-it-button" count-layout="horizontal"></a><script type="text/javascript" src="http://assets.pinterest.com/js/pinit.js"></script>
