<h3 class="title">About Nellie Huang</h3>
<a href="http://www.nelliehuang.com">Nellie Huang</a> is the co-founder of WildJunket. As a professional travel writer with a special interest in offgrid destinations and adventure travel, she scours through the world in search for a slice of undiscovered paradise. In her quest, she's climbed an active volcano in Guatemala, swam with sealions in the Galapagos and built a school in Tanzania. <div class="profile-link">
